            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Google's Largest Contentful Paint (LCP) metric almost always measures an element above the fold. Slow above-the-fold rendering directly hurts Core Web Vitals scores, which are a Google ranking factor. Above-the-fold ad density is also penalised by the intrusive-interstitials update.</p></div></div>
          </div>
